      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just not true though. i don't have anyone here. i've been here a year and i've made zero real connections. it's like i'm a ghost. a ghost just walking around a crowded city. it honestly feels less like i'm \"lonely\" and more like i'm just... unnecessary. like the world is just better off without the extra clutter of my life.",
